<p>This was originally going to be a 001 proposal. I became disillusioned with that, so thought I'd publish the bulk of it as a tale instead. My first tale, in fact. (With that in mind, I hope I've done everything properly).</p>
<p>With thanks to the following:</p>
<p>SpookyPizza<br />
Varaxous<br />
MrWrong<br />
halitherses</p>
<p>This tale contains lots of poetical references, and lots of crosslinks. I will remove any crosslinks at the request of the original authors.</p>

